Transforming the 5 minute mattress test drive into a private 120 day in home experience.




It is our daily mantra to eliminate the traditional friction that is so common between vendors and consumers by offering extreme courtesy coupled with clear and transparent policies...label us truly "consumer centric". We offer the friendliest 120 day home trial in the business: if you're not happy, you have the option to return our bed and only be responsible for the original delivery charge. No penalty fees, no pickup fees. Simply a refund. Additionally, in the rare instance that you may have ordered incorrectly for your needs be it size or comfort, we are glad to honor an exchange within the 120 day home trial for only the cost of delivery as a courtesy to you. 

   Enjoy peace of mind with our 15 year warranty



 Best Reviewed Mattress
We've won BBB's award for excellence in website marketing messages



Learn More



We guarantee that your mattress is crafted fresh, to our strict specifications. All mattresses are thoroughly inspected before being sent out for delivery to your home.






      We're confident your expectations will be exceeded from the day of delivery and beyond as our product continues to perform for you. By educating our customers on the features and benefits of our ultra premium bed with 'objective measures of comparison', we have had great success without ever having to use high pressure or confusing tactics. This approach results in a minuscule amount of returns. 
   


     We offer the friendliest 120 day home trial in the luxury mattress market. If you find that our bed is not right for you, it can be returned for a full and prompt refund of the purchase price, less the original delivery fee. No penalty fees, pick-up fees or restocking fees (we NEVER re-stock a mattress). In offering this friendly policy, we do ask that you double-check your measurements before you buy to confirm that the mattress and foundation heights you've chosen fit your needs.
   



     Keep in mind, for over 30 years people have been buying mattresses through infomercials and/or by phone. Today the Internet makes this process so much easier and more informative with websites such as Saatva's. You can simply make a decision at your own pace with absolutely no pressure from a salesperson, no insult by the falseness of a phony sale, and no gimmicks that are historically found in retail mattress stores.
   


At Saatva, we are serious about quality and maintaining our pristine reputation. If our mattress or any aspect of Saatva disappoints you, please click or call us immediately for the remedy. We constantly monitor all comments on our site and on the Internet.  Please know we are vigilant with action on addressing any blatant or perceived misstatements about Saatva.  Let's be friendly and just click or call for happiness!  
   




































