About Beautyrest
Beautyrest
Beautyrest is the flagship sub-brand that made Simmons what it is today. Beautyrest is so popular, in fact, that it has evolved to have sub-brands of its own. Beautyrest Black, Beautyrest Platinum, and Beautyrest Silver represent the leading models from Simmons Bedding Company today.
Simmons Beautyrest strikes an excellent balance of quality and value, making it one of the most popular and successful mattress brands in the world. With a range of price points from under $500 to over $5,000, every size from Twin to Queen to California King, and every Comfort Scale rating from 1 to 10, you can rest assured there is a Simmons Beautyrest mattress perfect for you!
Beautyrest Black
Beautyrest Black is the top-of-the-line series from Simmons. These high-end mattresses feature the best comfort materials and luxury features that Simmons has to offer. If you want to make an investment in luxury sleep, Beautyrest Black is a great option.
Beautyrest Black mattresses feature SurfaceCoolPlus Fiber quilts to help regulate temperature and keep you comfortably cool. Next, strategic layers of AirCool Gel Memory Foam, BlackIce Memory Foam, Comfort Response Latex, Dynamic Response Memory Foam, Micro Diamond Memory Foam, and/or GelTouch Foam are used to provide optimal comfort, support, and temperature control for ideal sleep. BlackIce Memory Foam and Micro Diamond Memory Foam include actual diamond particles within the memory foam as a hyperconducting enhancement to absorb body heat and disperse it across the entire mattress surface. This eliminates pockets of trapped body heat for cooler, more comfortable sleep. Lastly, Veriform Advanced Pocketed Coils form the support base of the mattress, utilizing triple wire braided coils to provide durable, precise support while significantly limiting the transfer of motion. If you're ready for the best sleep of your life, Beautyrest Black is the solution.

SurfaceCoolPlus Fiber cover
Micro Diamond Memory Foam
Advanced Pocketed Coil system
Ventilated AirCool BeautyEdge

Beautyrest Platinum
Beautyrest Platinum exists at the crossroads of affordability and high-end quality for those who desire Beautyrest Black luxury, but don't have the budget for it. Beautyrest Platinum models feature some, but not all, of the comfort materials you'll find in Beautyrest Black, and use a more cost-effective support system. By leaving out some of the more lavish features, Beautyrest Platinum achieves a good balance of value and luxury.

SurfaceCoolPlus Fiber cover
AirCool MAX Memory Foam
Beautyrest Pocketed Coil system
Ventilated AirCool BeautyEdge

Beautyrest Silver
Beautyrest Silver mattresses are an excellent option for discerning customers who want a great value on a quality mattress. These mattresses are surprisingly affordable, and backed by the quality you would expect from Simmons Beautyrest. Beautyrest Silver replaces the Beautyrest Recharge series, but maintains the technology and features that made it so popular, in addition to some new ones. Beautyrest Silver boasts a dependable support system, advanced comfort foams, and contains actual silver to help wick away moisture, conduct and disperse body heat, and repel microorganisms.

DualCool Fiber cover
AirCool Memory Foam
Beautyrest Pocketed Coil System
Ventilated AirCool BeautyEdge

Beautyrest Silver Hybrid
Simmons Beautyrest Silver Hybrid models boast the same technology as Beautyrest Silver, but with a hybrid design. Beautyrest Silver Hybrid mattresses combine 1,000 Density Beautyrest Pocketed Coil systems with advanced memory foam layers to achieve cool, comfortable, and supportive sleep.












