Beauty Sleep
Beauty Sleep Video
Our Experts


Affordable Quality and Comfort
Simmons Beautysleep mattresses represent some of the greatest values in the industry because they often contain the same materials found in mattresses sold at much higher price points. Select BeautySleep models provide sturdy support through an individually pocketed coil system made from high carbon steel. This coil system contours to the curves of the body exceptionally well, and it also helps individuals maintain proper spinal alignment while they sleep. Some BeautySleep models include premium comfort materials like Gel Touch, which features a unique combination of memory foam and gel to enhance overall support and alleviate pressure points that can lead to tossing and turning. Gel is one of the most durable materials used in mattresses today, and it can substantially extend the comfort life of a mattress. This means that a BeautySleep mattress with Gel Touch will retain its showroom level of comfort for a longer period of time than a comparable model not containing gel.
An Exceptional Value
Simmons ensures that sleepers enjoy uniform comfort and support by surrounding each BeautySleep mattress with a three inch foam encasement. The foam encasement ensures that each sleeper will feel comfortable and supported whether he or she sleeps in the middle or on the edge of the mattress. BeautySleep mattresses are a great choice for budget minded individuals looking for the best value in a quality mattress. Whether you prefer a stiff and rigid sleep experience, or you're more comfortable sinking into a plush or pillow top, there's a BeautySleep mattress that can give you night after night of deep, restful sleep. Shop today, and find the right BeautySleep mattress for you!




      Looking for an easy way to find the perfect mattress? When you work with our mattress experts, you have the benefit of shopping with the most knowledgeable team in the industry. Our mattress experts are continually training with manufacturers to learn the ins and outs of the latest mattresses and sleep technologies so that they can recommend the ideal mattress for your budget and lifestyle. Just tell our experts what you're looking for in a mattress, and they'll help you find the model that is best suited for the way you sleep. Whether you're purchasing your first mattress, or you're replacing one you've slept on for years, our friendly experts make it easy for you to make a confident purchase. 
    

      At US-Mattress, we're committed to providing a pleasant and easy shopping experience, which is why you'll never feel pressured into making a purchase. Your total sleep satisfaction is our goal, and our experts are here to help you in any way they can. Contact a friendly mattress expert today, and start enjoying the deep, restful sleep that you deserve! 
    












